Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt the engines!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.71,0:00:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.78,0:00:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's smooth so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.21,0:00:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But is this really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Metalhead just annihilated all the whalesquids!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Metalhead! Ledo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All Hideauze in the area have been exterminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Get those Yunboros out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The legendary treasure's all ours now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The shaft's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, take your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.84,0:03:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice! Looking good over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinion, check this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the catch's gonna be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, I wanted to drink this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How d'you like it? And this is just the tip of the iceberg!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:48.14,Default,,0,250,0,,So this is the heritage our great ancestors have left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:50.14,Default,,0,0,90,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:04:54.52,Default,,0,0,90,,There's even better stuff buried deep inside the whalesquids' lair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.98,Default,,0,0,90,,Just like my brother said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:04:59.80,Default,,0,0,90,,No rust at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:02.08,Default,,0,0,90,,And there's a whole mountain of this stuff down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:06.13,Default,,0,0,90,,These treasures will let us restore the world to its former glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:09.12,Default,,0,0,90,,Restore the {\i1}world{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.90,Default,,0,0,90,,We're the ones who found this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:12.70,Default,,0,0,90,,{\move(640,630,640,685,200,1000)}It's {\i1}our{\i0} treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here because I wanted to use this heritage for the benefit of all mankind—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's the point if we don't benefit from it first?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Others are just going to try to take it from us if we keep it all to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got plenty of firepower right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be afraid of!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone butts in, we'll kick their asses!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!{無電を打つ, included in next line}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Send out a message that we annihilated the whalesquids and got the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You'd only provoke the ships in the area!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just warning them so they don't poke their noses in our stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Maximum range! Get it ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention to all ships receiving this message!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We've annihilated all the whalesquids nesting in the Sea of Fog!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole shoal's dead, and their nest is gone too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Pinion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember me as Pinion of the Sea of Fog!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,To all you out there who wanted the treasure in the whalesquids' nest:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even think of trying anything funny now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The treasure's all ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a warning to all ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We will sink any approaching vessel without mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinion does have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt that the pirates will show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to build up our firepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does everyone assume this will end up in conflict?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Flange,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you have a delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand it over.{sounds harsh. maybe "Let me see it."?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:07:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Ledo killed all the whalesquids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Are we gonna be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure this is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{overlap}Enough—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With Ledo and Chamber on our side, we are able to delve into the whalesquids' nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That much is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.06,0:07:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But instead of trading our new-found treasures with other ships,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,we threaten to attack anyone that approaches?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ludicrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna end up as outcasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship owners under my command \Nhave begun listening to Pinion as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We certainly do need his abilities as a mechanic to properly utilize what we salvage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't give up even if I tried stopping him.{Possible comma before "even" here, if what follows is nonrestrictive (and it may be).}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you helping us out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be able to handle salvaging without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The shaft's blocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Open it up with the Metalhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you, Ledo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you lost your nerve?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Lost my nerve? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I annihilated the Hideauze!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Joe! That's enough for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore, has the new layout of the fleet been finalized?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The ship owners were all very cooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left now is to relink the ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no small task, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore, did you hear Pinion's broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your honest opinion about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Until there's evidence that he's telling the truth, there's no need to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Has the news spread among the fleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Every soul probably knows by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Some ship owners might become jealous and decide to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:10:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I will respect their decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Ordum, is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Ledo destroyed the whalesquids' nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I heard Pinion's broadcast myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How terribly foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I said I wanted to avenge my brother?{ep7}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that was nothing but a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how Melty's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they're fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinion's just bragging.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:10:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Amy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.24,0:11:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{halftime}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:30.26,Default,,0,0,90,,Any signs that they'll surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.26,0:11:31.49,Default,,0,0,90,,None whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:33.12,Default,,0,0,90,,Aren't they just out of ammo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:34.34,Default,,0,0,90,,Don't stop firing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:35.39,Default,,0,0,90,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:37.80,Default,,0,0,90,,We've got plenty of ammo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:42.38,Default,,0,0,90,,{\i1}They{\i0} attacked {\i1}us{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.90,Default,,0,0,90,,Are we gonna sink them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:45.94,Default,,0,0,90,,If they don't surrender, then yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:46.81,Default,,0,0,90,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:49.56,Default,,0,0,90,,The treasure's repairs should be done by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:51.81,Default,,0,0,90,,Let's give them a taste of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A bit more! A bit more! A bit more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:12:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All set!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Easier said than done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this it? Or that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're surrendering!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,About time, those fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, why even bother struggling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you get for picking a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, spare us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll hand over all the culprits!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us join you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we took in every mob that makes the same request,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the platoon would just get bigger and—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If we expanded the fleet in this way, we'd become invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's still a bunch of stuff that needs to be hauled up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather those who want to join!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we got ourselves a deal here, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Lock this one up somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like to check the stuff we pulled up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,With, uh... the Metalhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What d'you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Use of equipment outside of missions requires the Lieutenant's authorization.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Heard that? You don't mind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's settled!{Possible comma after "Then" here. Xythar, you're really good at these, so without the audio/context, I'll leave it to you.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:13:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on then!{Xythar: same thing about this "then" comma.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do this without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Metalhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink up, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Those pirate ships who came looking for trouble have all surrendered!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Things have been going well for us since we made this place our stronghold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got Ledo and Chamber to thank for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you all better kiss that Metalhead's ass!{Xythar: possible comma after this "Now."}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For what purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.77,0:15:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For whose sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When did it begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was it when I woke up beneath these foreign skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was it when I first got into Chamber, a Machine Caliber?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or maybe when I first came into this world?{i don't think there's a second time you come into this world}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a primitive EMP weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,EMP? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Its basic construction is similar to my beam weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:16:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,However, its output is estimated to be 1/50th that of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,1/50th of yours is still huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It is approximately 76 times the current combined firepower of this fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Very nice indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.54,0:16:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we make it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Repairs might make reactivation possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,However, firing it requires tremendous amounts of electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Electricity, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Could we make it work with lightbugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Further analysis required.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell Ledo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I have found evidence corroborating the footage of{regarding} the Hideauze's background.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the lightbugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The lightbugs are nanomachines.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They are in fact identical to the exoskeleton of the Hideauze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They absorb electromagnetic waves and convert them to energy very efficiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, they self-replicate and form pseudo-carbon bonds,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,which allows them to form a solid exoskeleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This proves that Hideauze are a result of mankind's augmented evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes my and the whole Galactic Alliance's war completely meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Your understanding is logically unsound.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Hideauze are evolved humans, should I still be fighting them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any meaning in doing so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:18:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If there isn't, I can't fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't kill those living beings!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.49,0:18:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Your understanding denies both your existence and mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.64,0:18:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The newborn whalesquids...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind's fighting against itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the truth behind our war!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This additional information does not warrant a cessation of the Hideauze's annihilation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.51,0:18:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hideauze threaten to drive mankind to extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Preventing that is your only mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of the Alliance's propaganda!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.22,0:18:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My parallel link to the Alliance has been cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What I have said was the conclusion drawn from my own analysis of the available data.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.00,0:19:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind and the Hideauze will never come to an understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.46,0:19:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That is because they have rejected civilization itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If mankind possessed bodies as tough and powerful as those of the Hideauze,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,there would have been no need to develop Machine Calibers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My system is the product of mankind's knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we are necessary to mankind in order to augment their weak bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be surmised that mankind advanced their intellect and founded civilization
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to overcome their own limitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Civilization itself is proof that mankind stands at the apex of all creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the Hideauze have abandoned their human forms, along with their bodily limitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To merely pursue and satisfy one's well-being and desires as a biological creature,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,a higher level of intelligence is not necessarily required.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Machine Calibers are the only means for mankind to remain itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.84,0:20:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the result of pure knowledge given birth to by civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hideauze abandoned that very same knowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and thus became the culmination of biological beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying the Hideauze are ultimate lifeforms?{CARS?!}{Xythar: possible comma here after "So"}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You must therefore fight with me for the dignity of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.49,0:20:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In a conflict between creatures that are fundamentally the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,defeat is equivalent to annihilation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.06,0:20:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,One pursues civilization, \Nand the other abandons it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The war between the Galactic Alliance and the Hideauze
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is a conflict between two irreconcilable survival strategies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The vanquished will fall prey to natural selection.{we guilty crown now}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.26,0:20:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Selection...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you wish to survive, you have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.97,0:21:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're compelling me to fight?{Xythar: possible comma here after "So"}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.01,0:21:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You, a machine, are telling me, a human, what to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I am but an interface system that supports and oversees the development of pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I exist solely to set you up for success.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.50,0:21:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Polarized photon sequence received.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.11,0:21:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It is an Alliance-standard encrypted transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.28,0:21:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Identified as an allied unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,An allied unit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Kugel...
